    title: 'The First Console War',
    subtitle: 'How Mattel challenged Atari in 1979, Coleco gatecrashed in 1982, and the three-way fight ended when all of them lost',
    category: 'history',
    summary: 'A decade before SNES versus Genesis, the first major console war was fought between Atari\'s 2600, Mattel\'s Intellivision, and Coleco\'s ColecoVision. The winner of every round was eliminated by the 1983 crash.',
